&lt;br /&gt;
Your genetic test kit is almost on its way, and we&amp;#39;ll be sending you a separate email with the tracking information as soon as your kit ships!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Inside, it&amp;rsquo;ll contain everything you need to perform the test, including a pre-paid return envelope for your sample.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Once received, it typically takes between 3-6 weeks to analyze your genetic code and provide personalized recommendations based on your results. This time frame can be longer based on demand here at 10X Health.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You will receive a comprehensive PDF report of your results through email. This report will provide you with a clear and detailed understanding of your genetic code and how it affects your health.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
